org.apache.poi.hslf.blip

Class Bitmap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hslf.usermodel.HSLFPictureData
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.blip.Bitmap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, PictureData
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DIB, JPEG, PNG 

    public abstract class Bitmap
extends HSLFPictureData
    Represents a bitmap picture data: JPEG or PNG. The data is not compressed and the exact file content is written in the stream.(代表位图图片数据：JPEG或PNG。数据未被压缩，确切的文件内容被写入流中。)
